    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "997、998……999……これで1000回！\n今日も日課の腹筋終わり……ふぅ～……！",
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛は本当に凄いな……毎日1000回も\n腹筋するなんて、俺には真似出来ないよ",
      "startTime": 20.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！　お疲れ様です！\nええっと、もしかしてずっと見てました……？",
      "startTime": 28.2981098493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、悪い。覗き見するつもりはなかったんだが\n真剣に鍛えてたから声を掛け辛くて……",
      "startTime": 36.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、おかげで確信出来たよ。今日持って来た仕事は\n筋トレに励む愛にしか出来ないものだ",
      "startTime": 44.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "筋トレに励む私だから出来るお仕事……？\nジムのCMですか？　それともプロテインの広告……？",
      "startTime": 51.4666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "女子プロレス団体『DDP――ドラゴンドリーム\nプロレス』のオファーをもらってきたんだよ",
      "startTime": 61.1666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！？　プロレスって言いましたか！？\nあ、あのリングで戦う競技ですよね！？",
      "startTime": 66.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "む、むむむ、無理ですよ！　いくら腹筋が出来ても\nプロレスラーの方となんて絶対に並び立てません！",
      "startTime": 73.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないよ。今回は愛の根性と筋肉と\n絶対に相性がいい仕事だと俺は思っている",
      "startTime": 81.6728451927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それにDDPには愛のファンも沢山いるらしくてな\nオファーを受けてくれたら絶対に盛り上がるぞ",
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなこと言われても～……\n嬉しくは思いますけど……う～ん……",
      "startTime": 97.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛ならきっと衣装も似合うはずだ\n自信を持って会場を盛り上げてほしい",
      "startTime": 105.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ううぅぅ～……私がリングに立つなんて！？\n絶対すぐコテンパンにされちゃうよ～……",
      "startTime": 112.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "筋トレはそれなりに出来るけど……技？\nっていうのかな、全然知らないし、経験ないし……",
      "startTime": 119.8528732072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "おーい……聞いてるか、愛……？　ずっとぶつぶつ\n何か言っているがそんなに嫌なら断っても……",
      "startTime": 129.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……な、なんでもないですっ！　やりますっ！\nめずらしいお仕事ですし、こんな機会ないですし！",
      "startTime": 135.9999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが持ってきてくれた\n私だけのお仕事ですから！　当然、頑張りますよ！",
      "startTime": 141.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "どんなお仕事でも完璧にこなしてみせます！\nリズノワとして、アイドルとして……BIG4として！",
      "startTime": 149.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "やけに緊張しているな……ラウンドガールの仕事は\n別にめずらしくないと思ったんだが……",
      "startTime": 158.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "よし、もっともっと鍛えなきゃ。プロレスラーの方と\n並んでも恥ずかしくないよう、完璧に仕上げないと！",
      "startTime": 165.5838322322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか……筋肉を愛するからこそ、中途半端な）\n（仕上がりで選手の前に立つのが恥ずかしかったのか）",
      "startTime": 174.7666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで気負わなくても大丈夫だよ\nいつも通り、愛らしくやってくれればいいんだ",
      "startTime": 181.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……分かりました！\nいつも通り頑張ります！　この筋肉でっ！",
      "startTime": 187.732255848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 192.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……よし、15㎞のランニングも完走！\n腹筋1500回も達成……スクワットも500回……",
      "startTime": 200.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（ラウンドガールの仕事を引き受けてから）\n（愛のトレーニングが明らかに過激になっているぞ）",
      "startTime": 208.7862117305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（今のところ他の仕事に支障はないが）\n（やり過ぎないか心配で見に来てしまった……）",
      "startTime": 215.3333445232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "ウォーミングアップ終わり！　ご褒美にラーメン……と\n言いたいけどプロテイン飲んでもっと追い込んで……",
      "startTime": 223.0666778565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て、今のがウォーミングアップ！？　これ以上に\nどんな過酷なトレーニングをするつもりなんだ！？",
      "startTime": 230.8333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、見ていてくれたんですか！\nふふ、どうです、この腹筋のライン、ムッキムキです！",
      "startTime": 237.3000111898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "うおっ……ど、どうなってるんだその腹筋……\nキレが凄過ぎる。まるで美しい彫刻みたいだ……",
      "startTime": 246.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_12_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえっ、プロレスラーの方に比べたら\nこんなのまだまだ全然ですっ！",
      "startTime": 254.6666778565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
